tourBios.otherInfo: Had conditional status on the 2000 BUY.COM TOUR, but did not play an event...Has no prior experience on the BUY.COM TOUR...Played in 13 events on the Japan Golf Tour in 2000. His only three top-25s came in consecutive starts from late June to mid-July. Best of the three was a T13 at the Aiful Cup. Ranked 115th on the 2000 Japan Golf Tour money list...Has played in one PGA TOUR event, the 1998 Greater Greensboro Chrysler Classic, missing cut...As an amateur, had made cut in three of four events on the Japan Golf Tour...A T23 in the 1998 Token Corporation Cup was his prior best finish...Captain of the golf team at the University of Japan...Made it to the final stage of both the PGA TOUR and Japan Golf Tour Qualifying Schools in 1999...Has one hole-in-one in competitive rounds.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Web.com Tour was T22nd in 2001 at the BUY.COM Fort Smith Classic.
